data.meta_description: Japanese Common Words 10000-12000 - Free download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. This document contains Japanese words and terms with brief English definitions. Some of the words relate to clothing, locations, time periods, emotions, professions, and other everyday topics. The document serves as a reference list for understanding common Japanese terminology in various contexts.
